Package com.rjrudin.marklogic.modulesloader.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssetFileFilter
    Simple implementation that accepts every file and ignores any directory starting with ".".
    BaseModulesFinder
    Abstract implementation that provides implementations for loading all the different kinds of modules, but doesn't actually implement findModules.
    DefaultExtensionMetadataProvider  
    DefaultModulesFinder
    Default implementation that loads all of the different kinds of REST modules.
    DefaultModulesLoader
    Uses the REST API for loading all modules except "assets", which are loaded via XCC for speed reasons.
    PropertiesModuleManager  
    TestServerModulesFinder
    Search options and REST properties are specific to a REST API server.
    XccAssetLoader
    Handles loading assets - as defined by the REST API, which are typically under the /ext directory - via XCC.
